WEBVTT

00:00.025 --> 00:01.479
Previously on
<i>Suits...</i>

00:01.504 --> 00:02.968
I'm bonding
with your father here.

00:02.969 --> 00:04.661
- Speaking of which--
- You're not taking it easy

00:04.662 --> 00:05.792
on me, are you?
A little.

00:06.051 --> 00:07.351
You mean something to me.

00:07.419 --> 00:09.270
You've always meant something
to me

00:09.354 --> 00:12.140
and you always will mean
something to me.

00:12.224 --> 00:14.442
What do you need, Harvey?

00:14.526 --> 00:16.059
Ava Hessington.

00:16.111 --> 00:17.945
I am not losing to him.

00:18.030 --> 00:19.197
You.

00:19.264 --> 00:22.066
Your blood feud
or whatever it is

00:22.117 --> 00:24.067
you have with that man
is what put the target

00:24.092 --> 00:25.546
on my back in the first place.

00:25.571 --> 00:28.295
I made this mess.
It's up to me to clear it up.

00:28.969 --> 00:31.300
Harvey and Cameron made a deal
to take you down.

00:31.318 --> 00:34.032
And part of that deal
was that I got to be the one

00:34.033 --> 00:35.200
to tell you about it.

00:35.284 --> 00:36.845
If he can't practice law
in the country,

00:36.852 --> 00:38.132
he can't be a member
of our firm.

00:38.187 --> 00:39.788
You set this whole thing up.

00:39.855 --> 00:41.823
Jessica set
this whole thing up.

00:41.874 --> 00:44.525
And, Edward,
we may be getting a divorce,

00:44.577 --> 00:47.128
but I fully intend on keeping
ownership of the house.

